nodes.title: Troubleshooting
widgets_values:
Troubleshooting animation:
    1) Change seed (987654321 ‚Üí  987654322)
    2) Lower QR Code start percent (0.300 ‚Üí 0.000)
    3) Lower SparseCtrl motion scale (1.000 ‚Üí 0.000)
    4) Lower IPAdapter ClipVision Enhancer weight (0.80 ‚Üí 0.60)
    5) Lower IPAdapter ClipVision Enhancer ratio (1.00 ‚Üí 0.50)

== Models Available through the Manager ==

vae-ft-mse-84000-ema-pruned.safetensors



== Motion Loras Manual Downloads ==
Go to this link and download the following Loras: 
https://huggingface.co/peteromallet/poms-funtime-mlora-emporium/tree/main

* WAS26.safetensors
* LiquidAF-0-1.safetensors

Place these in the folder:
Models/animatediff_motion_lora

Modified from:
== Image Travel SparseCtrl Hyper 03 ==
Originally posted on the Bonadoco's Discord
https://discord.com/channels/1076117621407223829/1283160652357173359/1283160652357173359

IPAdapter ClipVision Enhancer Batch
    Model: IPAdapter PLUS (high strength)
    Weight: 0.80
    Enhance Ratio: 1.00

AnimateDiff v3
    Context Options: pyramid
    Beta Schedule: avg(sqrt_linear,linear)
    Sample Settings: FreeNoise (OFF)

Motion Lora - WAS26: 0.600
Motion Lora - LiquidAF: 0.400

KSampler
    * Steps: 8, CFG: 0.8
    Sampler: LCM, Scheduler: SGM Uniform

Lora - SparseCtlr: 0.80
Lora - Hyper SD 8-Steps: 0.80

SparseCtrl
    Motion Scale: 1.000
    Start Percent: 0.000
    End Percent: 0.300

QR Code ControlNet
    Strength: 1.20
    Start Percent: 0.300
    End Percent: 1.000

128 frames
* Draft Settings - Steps: 8, CFG: 0.8
* HQ Settings - Steps: 12-14, CFG: 1.2-1.4
Put Latent Noise in White areas of mask

nodes.title: Total Frames
widgets_values: Total Frames = ((Hold Length + Transition Length) * Number of Images) + End Padding Frames
